Package com.google.auto.factory

Annotation Interface Provided

@Target(PARAMETER) public @interface Provided
An annotation to be applied to parameters that should be provided by an injected Provider in a generated factory.

The @Inject and Provider classes come from either the legacy package javax.inject or the updated package jakarta.inject. jakarta.inject is used if it is on the classpath. Compile with -Acom.google.auto.factory.InjectApi=javax if you want to use javax.inject even when jakarta.inject is available.
